  <section class="docstring">


        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">This = T = <a href="#t:wxGraphicsMatrix/0">wxGraphicsMatrix</a>()</pre>

        </div>


<p>Concatenates the matrix passed with the current matrix.</p><p>The effect of the resulting transformation is to first apply the transformation in <code class="inline">t</code> to
the coordinates and then apply the transformation in the current matrix to the coordinates.</p>
  </section>
</section>
